
Afsax n wayyur d afsax i d-iḍerrun yal mi ara yili [[Ayyur (itri)|wayyur]] deffir neγ deg tili n [[Akal|lqaεa]]. D asdari n wayyur γef [[Iṭij|yiṭij]], imi tezga-yas-d lqaεa. Taluft-a tḍerru-d yal tikkelt ara yemlil wayyu, lqaεa akked yiṭij deg yiwet n tizzirga.
